For sprite editing:
aseprite
Pixelorama 

Assets:
The Spriter's Resource - Has sprite sheets from classic GBC games you can study
OpenGameArt.org - Filter for 8-bit/pixel art assets that fit GBC constraints
GB Studio assets - https://gbstudio.dev has a built-in sprite editor and many free assets you can use

Sounds: use BGB to rip sounds